                    The aims of the pilgrimage are the following:
                    1.  That  the  most  holy  Heart  of  Jesus  free  our  society
               from  spiritual  and  temporal  evils  as  well  as  from  divine
               punishments;
                    2. That the holy Church grow in holiness and freedom;
                    3. That the dissident nations return to the holy Church;
                    4. To save and sanctify the Catholic nations, especially
               Italy and France;
                    5.  That  the  missionary  institutions  flourish  for  the
               salvation of the people who do not know Jesus Christ;
                    6. To dissipate the heresies and the sects which oppose   463
               the holy Church and the divine truths;
